// `emit_classify.vl` — the emitter's TYPE CLASSIFIERS and their supporting
// state: the `expr*`/`let*`/`declared*`/`param*`/`fnRet*`/`global*` families
// that resolve what VL type/rep a binding or expression lowers as, the
// narrowing and scope-slot bookkeeping they consult, and the shape/ref-list/
// literal-atom interning primitives they intern into on first sight. Reads the
// AST arena (`ast.vl`) and the shared emitter state (`emit_state.vl`); writes
// no bytes. Carved out of `wasmEmit.vl` (review N18).

